{
  "about": "Presidio-hardened Azure baseline for ScoutSuite. CIS-aligned, fail-closed: high-impact storage/SQL/network/identity controls are forced to 'danger'. Rule filenames track the pinned upstream ScoutSuite version declared in requirements.lock; CI validates every referenced rule against the policy/azure.rules.txt inventory before release.",
